3.2 Human rights

The Business Conduct Guidelines Our commitment to respecting human rights is anchored in our

Siemens Business Conduct Guidelines (BCGs) COMPLIANCE AND ETHICS. They set out the fundamental principles and rules that apply to our actions relating to human rights in our company and with our customers, external partners, and the public. The BCGs are binding for all employees worldwide. In addition, the Siemens Group Code of Conduct for Suppliers and Third-Party Intermediaries (Supplier Code of Conduct), which is mainly focused on rules of conduct relating to human rights, applies to the companyâ€™s suppliers, third-party intermediaries, and business partners.